These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: skydiving, drawing, fishing
1. Hobby:drawing is on the right of Hobby:fishing##1
2. Hobby:skydiving is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:skydiving is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Hobby   | fishing | drawing | skydiving |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Cigar: vegafina, pall-mall, bongani
1. Cigar:pall-mall is in an odd position##4
2. Cigar:vegafina is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Cigar   | vegafina | bongani | pall-mall |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Pet: ferret, mouse, hedgehog
1. Pet:mouse is in an even position##4
2. Pet:mouse is on the left or right of Pet:hedgehog##3
3. Pet:hedgehog is on the right of Pet:mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Pet   | ferret | mouse | hedgehog |

 #################################
 
